                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18401019-2634-offence-1 t18401019-cd-218"></join>3rd of August</rs>, 2 pieces of foreign gold coin called doubloons, value 6<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 12<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; and 2 dollars, value 8<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the monies of <persName id="t18401019-name-1175" type="victimName">
